{"tid":1268982,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［普世價值］十字軍東征","createTime":"2019-06-30T12:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T12:20:17.000Z","uid":28224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee13f8cf5ca1010df11d045b567374786c7ac2a","tid":1268982,"uid":28224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:16:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%8D%81%E5%AD%97%E8%BB%8D%E6%9D%B1%E5%BE%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25AD%2597%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%259D%25B1%25E5%25BE%2581&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=e68d8008\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/%E5%8D%81%E5%AD%97%E8%BB%8D%E6%9D%B1%E5%BE%81</a><br />\n十字軍東征（拉丁語：Cruciata；伊斯蘭世界稱為法蘭克人入侵；1096年－1291年）。這是一系列在羅馬天主教教皇的准許下的戰役，由西歐的封建領主和騎士對他們認為是異教徒的國家（地中海東岸）發動持續近200年的宗教戰爭。十字軍東征最初參與成員，例如：騎士、商人、農民，多數是自願的，受拜占庭帝國之邀，參與奪回聖地戰爭。這些十字軍也非拜占庭帝國主力部隊。東正教徒也參加其中幾次十字軍。"},{"pid":"43ded6f60d57ce30512887275c70adaa9cda4c82","tid":1268982,"uid":92908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:20:17.000Z","msg":"我帶路"}]}